# Normalize line endings so source checks out as LF on every platform.
#
# Nightly rustfmt enforces `newline_style = "Unix"` (see .rustfmt.toml).
# Without this, Windows CI runners check out *.rs with CRLF (their git
# default is core.autocrlf=true) and `cargo +nightly fmt --check` fails
# with "Incorrect newline style".
* text=auto
*.rs text eol=lf
